WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.190 align:middle line:90%


00:00:10.190 --> 00:00:12.920 align:middle line:84%
>> This is "Secret
Life of Symbols."

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:17.890 align:middle line:90%


